{"tid":1177223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外媒：和碩在印尼投資 10 億美元，組裝蘋果 iPhone 晶片","createTime":"2019-05-29T16:12:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T00:51:44.000Z","uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e1e51673e06948b309b46544d3de8ffd50c832ed","tid":1177223,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T16:12:07.000Z","msg":"外媒：和碩在印尼投資 10 億美元，組裝蘋果 iPhone 晶片<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2019/05/29/pegatron-indonesia-0-1-million-usd-iphone-chip/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2019%2F05%2F29%2Fpegatron-indonesia-0-1-million-usd-iphone-chip%2F&d=5SGopU86zwsNpZ2NEmuicvcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=b1787a65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2019/05/29/pegatron-indonesia-0-1-million-usd-iphone-chip/</a><br />\n<br />\n日本蘋果情報網站 iPhone Mania 引述路透社 28 日報導指出，印尼工業副部長 Warsito Ignatius 表示，台灣和碩已簽署意向書，將投資印尼的工廠 10 兆至 15 兆印尼盾（約 6.95 億至 10 億美元），組裝蘋果智慧手機 iPhone 用晶片。<br />\n<br />\n和碩之前似乎未曾生產過智慧手機晶片，而上述消息若為真，將是和碩首次生產智慧手機晶片。<br />\n<br />\nWarsito Ignatius 指出，和碩將和印尼電子公司 PT Sat Nusapersada 合作，於巴淡島的工廠進行晶片組裝。關於和碩上述投資，Warsito Ignatius 最先僅表示「將生產晶片」，不過之後進一步詳細說明稱「將組裝蘋果智慧手機用晶片」。<br />\n<br />\nWarsito Ignatius 並指出，「上述巴淡島工廠也可能將生產 MacBook 用零組件，但應該不會在短期內實施」。<br />\n<br />\n之前傳出和碩已和 PT Sat Nusapersada 合作，準備生產蘋果產品。和碩 28 日下跌 1.19%，收 50.0 元。"},{"pid":"1ccfd43260349b9efcba6e893b50bcde315f545a","tid":1177223,"uid":50776,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T16:23:10.000Z","msg":"新iphone實好臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f6affcd1acc0c2bd27610435bad495bcab22f4","tid":1177223,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T16:24:33.000Z","msg":"好嘢，又少樣嘢中國組裝"},{"pid":"f4aa474b781e638eeeb654cd904fd8f8a84ac5e0","tid":1177223,"uid":21432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T16:37:06.000Z","msg":"唔睇好，一陣勞資關係有少少問題就會俾的印尼狗無限放大，希望我估錯。"},{"pid":"9b8c6b954a69c93319d3c5d14352bded0466d32e","tid":1177223,"uid":73935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T16:51:41.000Z","msg":"兆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  聽到真係嚇死人"},{"pid":"8aaad20109ee910c98184a1ff33acc5cf311ac3e","tid":1177223,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T00:51:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}